# Amazon UI Clone

A simple and responsive Amazon homepage clone built using **HTML** and **CSS**.

---

![amazone ui](https://github.com/Alfa-07-debug/amazone_ui/blob/main/screenshot/ss1.jpg)
![amazone ui](https://github.com/Alfa-07-debug/amazone_ui/blob/main/screenshot/ss2.jpg)
![amazone ui](https://github.com/Alfa-07-debug/amazone_ui/blob/main/screenshot/ss3.jpg)




## Features

- Clean and simple design
- Responsive layout
- Amazon-like Navbar, Banners, Product Cards, and Footer
- Hover effects
- Mobile friendly

---

## Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3

---

## How to Run Locally

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Alfa-07-debug/amazone_ui.git


